	<td>6</td><td>8</td><td>2</td>
	<td>One number is correct and well-placed</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
	<td>#2</td>
	<td>6</td><td>1</td><td>4</td>
	<td>One number is correct and misplaced</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
	<td>#3</td>
	<td>2</td><td>0</td><td>6</td>
	<td>Two numbers are correct and misplaced</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
	<td>#4</td>
	<td>7</td><td>3</td><td>8</td>
	<td>No numbers are correct</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
	<td>#5</td>
	<td>8</td><td>7</td><td>0</td>
	<td>One number is correct and misplaced</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
	<td>&#xA0;</td><td></td><td></td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <div id="solution">
      <h2>Solution</h2>

      <ul>
	<li>#6: #4 + #5 mean 0 is a digit</li>
	<li>#7: #6 + #5 + #3 mean 0 is in the first position</li>
	<li>#8: #1 + #2 mean 6 is not a digit</li>
	<li>#9: #8 + #3 mean 2 is a digit</li>
	<li>#A: #9 + #8 + #1 mean 2 is in the last position</li>
	<li>#B: #A + #8 + #2 mean 4 is in the second position</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
